 <div class="title" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Model validation and historical climate</div>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The results presented here only focus on the following archipelagos: Fiji, Hawaii, New Caledonia, Papua New Guinea, Solomon Islands and Vanuatu. Under historical climate, areas of climatic suitability for 
  <span class="italic">M. peltata</span> were identified in Fiji, Papua New Guinea, Solomon Islands and Vanuatu (Fig. 
  <a rid="ece31915-fig-0003" ref-type="fig" href="#ece31915-fig-0003">3</a>). Changes in the area of climatic suitability for 
  <span class="italic">M. peltata</span> are shown in Table 
  <a rid="ece31915-tbl-0002" ref-type="table-wrap" href="#ece31915-tbl-0002">2</a>.
 </p>
